# Friday Implementation Plan

## Principles

- Backend remains the deterministic system of record.
- AI and workers are proposal/read-only only.
- All writes stay behind backend validation and the approval/action dispatcher.
- LINE remains export-based read-only.
- UX stays chat-native: Friday reports important progress in the chat surface, not hidden in a debug page.
- Tests are focused and proportional: build/lint plus smoke or unit tests only around changed risk.

